  Two rev bumps (one for the released viewcvs, one for the cvs snapshot) to
  address security bug #72461

  05 Sep 2004; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org>
  viewcvs-0.9.2_p20040831.ebuild:
  Fixed ChangeLog header. Added missing IUSE.

  03 Sep 2004; Renat Lumpau <rl03@gentoo.org> files/reconfig:
  The reconfig hook now cleans up after itself.

